{"tid":2257673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：香港要融入國家發展大局","createTime":"2020-10-25T11:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T12:24:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d2733f858395ad69981834a2ee3e1a383cb7a9b2","tid":2257673,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tGIIgwdrxBCHUrhuCc_i9A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/singtao.com.hk/b9afe985059b9c5ef88aededb3351f1c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtGIIgwdrxBCHUrhuCc_i9A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2Fb9afe985059b9c5ef88aededb3351f1c&h=625cfc5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】政務司司長張建宗表示，香港融入國家發展大局，並不是要將香港「內地化」、「邊緣化」，而是讓香港繼續發揮「一國兩制」的獨特優勢。他又強調大灣區為本港青年人提供一條就業和事業發展的新跑道，以及多一個選擇，鼓勵青年人親身了解國家發展及箇中契機，時刻保持開放包容和良性競爭的心態，發揮所長，好好利用大灣區這個廣闊的平台。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗發表網誌指，粵港澳大灣區不僅是國家開放程度最高、經濟活力最強的區域之一，其人均生產總值超過2.3萬美元，經濟發展水平顯著高於內地其他主要城市群。大灣區無論在人口、經濟規模和資源方面均具雄厚實力，是一個獨特多元的經濟體，地區生產總值達1.6萬億美元，以經濟規模論，可望在不久的未來，超越紐約灣區和東京灣區，成為世界上最大的灣區。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，香港站在新的歷史起點，要肩負新重任和新使命，與時俱進，憑藉「一國兩制」的獨特優勢，積極抓緊機遇，更好融入國家發展大局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港融入國家發展大局-張建宗-非內地化或邊緣化-031600934.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%9E%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%80-%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E9%9D%9E%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%96%E6%88%96%E9%82%8A%E7%B7%A3%E5%8C%96-031600934.html&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=92a1114d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港融入國家發展大局-張建宗-非內地化或邊緣化-031600934.html</a>"},{"pid":"986480bd81cde4d582f5c78faf60b094500bbd3c","tid":2257673,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f12a68477dbec6f8a5c555226ad3cb7376a3f49","tid":2257673,"uid":110562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"係咁用大灣區合併香港 好撚煩"},{"pid":"16246b2a2eca3f4bb3c2fa12698c84d2da1e1c9e","tid":2257673,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔搞鳩香港，港豬就晨早融入左啦"},{"pid":"dbeb306251b5f0fe841dafac783fdf9590eea694","tid":2257673,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"融晒香港庫房就有"},{"pid":"d1c9949f3d78333d121529797253fc6a2cd4e0f7","tid":2257673,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"而政務司司長張建宗則申報有９項本港物業，當中大部份由妻子名義持有，分布於中西區及東區，後者佔６個。其中7個屬住宅物業，2個商業。據傳媒去年的報導，張建宗及其妻持有包括豪宅單位，例如半山嘉富麗苑、北角DIVA及天后乘龍閣的單位，估值至少超過1.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n===========================<br />\n一間大灣區物業都無喎局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f345437968b102a7fa63548d2869394c93807f7e","tid":2257673,"uid":207972,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"淨係口號式咁吹，當真係有青年想去大灣區發展，有咩支援呀？"},{"pid":"8b3c747a8a955b8190813477eced25249bc352d1","tid":2257673,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"啱啱主席先一直唔想提香港，佢真係想觸怒聖上喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec9acc755a38296c3fc8813cb6734c61a616edd","tid":2257673,"uid":276548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"強烈要求 香港市政府 跟中共各階級官員 薪金接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e846842a929a7bcbcc35d09cf44c358ab839d040","tid":2257673,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"佢連支語都唔識"},{"pid":"18a9b6303e80ada33a8a0421d68bb1a1635c545d","tid":2257673,"uid":3104